You may get help on the following topics:
psireport - explains the psireport screen
advancement - explains how advancement works in the Guild
levels - gives the xp and gp chart for levels
powers - a quick reference chart to the powers with Guild Level and cost
emotes - a list of guild specific emotes
concentration - explains the concentration requirement
banishment - explains the process for guild punishment

You may get help on a particular power using 'phelp <power name>'.

just do phelp <topic>.  To get a list of psionicists online do 'psions'.  For
your guild statistics use 'psireport'.  To talk or emote on the guild chat
line use 'psi' or 'epsi' respectively.  
